{"tid":970519,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[中興華為之後] TCL爆資安疑慮 美國盯上","createTime":"2019-01-06T01:34:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-06T12:20:25.000Z","uid":141151,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2519d11ae20e5cf3bd5ec89d93c2ecbaea7ca947","tid":970519,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T01:34:12.000Z","msg":"TCL爆資安疑慮 美國盯上<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://money.udn.com/money/story/5603/3577026\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmoney.udn.com%2Fmoney%2Fstory%2F5603%2F3577026&d=ew77jXDyOYNVIOodbIO3mFzEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=5208b362\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://money.udn.com/money/story/5603/3577026</a><br />\n<br />\n繼華為、中興之後，下一個被美國盯上的中國企業TCL集團，因天氣App遭控收集全球智能手機用戶的海量數據，被質疑對用戶安全問題有疑慮。<br />\n<br />\nTCL第一時間回應，表示正進一步與合作夥伴和第三方檢測機構進行相關調查。<br />\n<br />\n參考消息網報導，美國對中國技術企業的抹黑似乎又有了新目標。據美國《華爾街日報》報導，谷歌應用商店中全球下載量最多的天氣應用軟體（App），是名為「Weather Forecast&mdash;World Weather Accurate Radar」（天氣預報──世界天氣準確雷達）的免費應用軟體，來自中國深圳TCL電信技術有限公司。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，這款天氣App是由TCL公司研發並預裝在阿爾卡特手機上，一直在收集全球智能手機用戶的海量數據。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">倫敦一家網路安全公司指控，這款天氣應用軟體是TCL透過在華服務器，收集包括智能手機用戶地理位置、電子郵箱地址和唯一的15位國際移動設備識別碼（IMEI）等數據，並強調對用戶數據「過度收集」。且在未經許可下，讓用戶訂閱一些付費才能使用的服務。</span><br />\n<br />\n參考消息網連繫TCL第一時間回應，TCL人士表示，對用戶安全問題十分重視，此款App收集的數據均為手機應用中常見的用戶最基本信息，并且經過用戶的同意，目的主要是提升使用體驗。TCL否認對用戶數據「過度收集」，強調說法並非事實。TCL人士還表示，這款App服務器在中國的說法也不是事實，因為使用的是亞馬遜AWS服務器，所有數據都在美國。<br />\n<br />\nTCL表示，正在進一步與合作夥伴和第三方檢測機構進行相關調查。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">中國現代國際關系研究院副研究員李崢認為，美國正在有目的性地尋找中國相關技術企業的漏洞，從而進行攻擊和抹黑。此次TCL事件正是美方有針對性地打壓中國技術企業的表現。</span>"},{"pid":"aaae7ccb3564080092e828e97225bb1efa50ac5f","tid":970519,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T01:37:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_b.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_g.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_p.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_y.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09daae04a636487d5c9965d3989ca9dc5ca0b6ae","tid":970519,"uid":18477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T02:05:56.000Z","msg":"俗語都有話<br />\n<br />\n上樑不正下樑歪"},{"pid":"2685efdc9af0cb9a116f8e47928e89f1c5fdc7f8","tid":970519,"uid":60120,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T02:18:16.000Z","msg":"講到咁清白，又唔改返要求少啲授權<br />\n係都要spin去國家層面話人恰自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n全部個腦都裝屎"},{"pid":"857f1ec2fa1dd559b3dfc7defaa993b22e92edc6","tid":970519,"uid":61280,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T02:22:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>悶唔撚悶D呀美帝又攪支那手機牌子？？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好心開新場郁軟件2大Keeper馬家軍啦屌！！！！</strong></span></span></span>"},{"pid":"c8da18eb542b3edf9c9fd957cbd3c9342ce8d34d","tid":970519,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T03:06:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e68d22320feb404a180686eb20f9c01c51404743","tid":970519,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T03:34:24.000Z","msg":"又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b23b7613b0c4287d263e572991a5a9c6b4f922c","tid":970519,"uid":36162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T03:52:06.000Z","msg":"TCL 係美國都賣好多LCD TV<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif